{"id": "1267931778379681803", "channel_id": "1266254397680386139", "type": 0, "author_id": "1045141709580927067", "author_name": "luoqixikiss", "author_bot": false, "content": "其实我觉得还是一个混沌比较好，因为血肉队狂气爆发需要吞噬胚胎，纯血肉队就要有4个角色分配胚胎(还有圣子胚胎)，这样玩起太抢手了。", "timestamp": "2024-07-30T19:48:12.999000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-07-30T19:49:06.431000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1266254397680386139", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超限版本下，純血肉隊伍的理論組成猜想", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681", "1174179734373019748"]}
